# OnlineOrNot Provider

The OnlineOrNot provider allows you to interact with the [OnlineOrNot](https://onlineornot.com) API to manage uptime monitoring resources including:

- **Uptime Checks** - Monitor website availability and response times
- **Heartbeats** - Monitor cron jobs and scheduled tasks  
- **Status Pages** - Create public status pages for your services
- **Webhooks** - Configure alert notifications
- **Maintenance Windows** - Schedule maintenance periods

